author: arkurth
msg: Updated Version_6.pm::run_sysprep() to reset some registry keys which prevent Sysprep from running if Sysprep had failed before.  Improved the cleanup tasks in this subroutine so that old logs are deleted before running Sysprep.  Changed the behavior after Sysprep is executed to detect unresponsiveness and power off instead of waiting for a fixed 180 seconds.
Added reg_add() to Windows.pm.  This gets called by Version_6.pm::run_sysprep().
